1
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:48,160
I didn't notice anything unusual about His Majesty.

2
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:50,440
Could it be some new trick?

3
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:53,040
Just a packet of powdered sugar.

4
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,680
Nothing new.

5
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,440
I don't understand.

6
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:03,640
Just a trick to test one's loyalty.

7
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:07,520
If Cangyue had given the powdered sugar to His Majesty,

8
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:11,600
she would be framing the Grand Princess of Donglin.

9
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,320
She would surely die.

10
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,120
Now that she has actually put the poison

11
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:19,880
into His Majesty's meals,

12
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,940
she has proven herself trustworthy.

13
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:24,720
How do you plan to use her?

14
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:29,000
Isn't His Majesty quite interested in this girl?

15
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,320
Go tell her

16
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:33,720
to keep His Majesty hooked.

17
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:38,200
Once he brings a woman to the court and disrupts the state affairs,

18
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:43,479
his important officials will surely turn their backs on him.

19
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:45,640
Then without you lifting a finger,

20
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:49,280
he will lose his throne.

21
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,160
Hahaha.

22
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,300
Now we just wait for him to fall into the trap.

23
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:02,360
Eldest Princess, Eunuch Sun.

24
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:05,640
Let's see how you eat this side dish.

25
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,280
So beautiful.

26
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,079
Your Majesty.

27
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:23,320
Let me see how your painting is going.

28
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:24,680
Want to see it?

29
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,440
Yes.

30
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,960
Hmph, you're terrible.

31
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:34,360
Your Majesty, where are we going to play later?

32
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,560
Where do you want to play?

33
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,090
I will accompany you there.

34
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:42,079
Then I want to play in your heart.

35
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,760
What a bad influence.

36
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,160
Absolutely ridiculous.

37
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,820
You've been standing for a while.

38
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:51,960
Speak.

39
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,360
Your Majesty.

40
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:56,320
It is time to select a new batch of palace maids.

41
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:59,250
After all, this concerns the stability of the state.

42
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:02,280
Your Majesty, the drought is ongoing.

43
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,200
Crops are failing everywhere.

44
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:06,920
I implore Your Majesty to issue a disaster relief decree immediately.

45
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,560
Do not indulge in beauty.

46
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,680
I disagree.

47
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:14,560
Your Majesty should take more concubines to fill the harem

48
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,200
to stabilize the court.

49
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,640
Enough.

50
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,160
I think Chancellor Zhou is right.

51
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,640
Aunt.

52
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:50,680
Having Cangyue is enough for me right now.

53
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,880
As for other matters,

54
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,800
I don't want to get involved.

55
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:59,200
Xuan, a monarch cannot be without an heir.

56
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:03,120
Selecting concubines early to consolidate the harem is what matters.

57
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:03,960
Ridiculous.

58
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:08,300
Most of the concubines and maids in his harem

59
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:12,680
are spies planted by the Grand Princess during the draft.

60
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,440
Aunt.

61
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,560
Your Majesty.

62
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,360
Your Majesty.

63
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,480
Your Majesty.

64
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:20,519
Quick, summon the royal physician.

65
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:31,760
Your Majesty, how can I live without you?

66
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,200
Am I not going to make it?

67
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:37,440
I will just watch you put on a show.

68
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:40,650
I haven't even had time to make you my consort.

69
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,240
I don't want to die.

70
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,560
So,

71
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,680
Just speak your mind.

72
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,640
It's this handkerchief.

73
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:18,560
This handkerchief clearly has Aunt's name on it.

74
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,960
This fabric is also unique in the palace.

75
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,440
Only Aunt uses it.

76
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:26,560
Aunt.

77
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,160
Why did you want to harm me?

78
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,560
Your Majesty, I am wronged.

79
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,960
Someone must be trying to frame me.

80
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,120
Frame you?

81
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,840
Who would dare frame you?

82
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:41,940
And who would dare use aunt's personal handkerchief to frame you?

83
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:44,760
The only one who can get close to His Majesty now

84
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,600
is this bitch.

85
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:49,760
Maybe she is the one trying to murder His Majesty.

86
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:52,560
Speak. Why did you do this?

87
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,280
You mean she did it?

88
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:08,840
Who would poison themselves while poisoning me?

89
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:12,300
Your Majesty, Her Highness has never been to your bedchamber.

90
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,040
I can testify for her.

91
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:17,600
Then how do you explain that handkerchief?

92
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:30,160
Your Majesty, I am truly innocent.

93
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,240
Although these methods are not clever,

94
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,600
letting him continue to cause trouble

95
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,760
won't do me any good.

96
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:39,560
Your Majesty.

97
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:42,770
His Highness would never do such a treasonous thing.

98
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:50,280
It seems this won't end without someone to take the blame.

99
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:54,040
That upright old man Shen Qingyan is also present.

100
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,240
Forget it.

101
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,360
It's him then.

102
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,080
Besides this woman,

103
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:08,240
the only person who can get close to the Emperor

104
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,040
is Eunuch Sun.

105
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,560
Your Majesty.

106
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,570
It wasn't me, Your Majesty.

107
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,400
Princess,

108
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,080
how can you slander me like this?

109
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,560
I am wholeheartedly devoted to you.

110
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:53,360
Sun Liang has followed His Majesty for so many years,

111
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,159
yet he dared to harm His Majesty.

112
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,320
As His Majesty's aunt,

113
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:59,120
I cannot turn a blind eye to this.

114
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,160
Guards, take him away.

115
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:09,560
Your Majesty.

116
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,360
Now that this traitor is dead,

117
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:15,400
please calm your anger.

118
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:16,840
Otherwise,

119
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:20,240
it would be bad for your health.

120
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:21,880
Investigate.

121
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:24,090
Investigate this thoroughly.

122
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,440
Find everyone connected to Sun Liang.

123
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:30,040
Even if you have to search the entire palace,

124
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,559
find anyone related to Sun Liang.

125
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:37,200
Your Majesty? Is there anything else, Aunt?

126
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,280
Your Majesty.

127
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:42,400
Since the truth has come to light,

128
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:47,240
I won't delay your grand plans any longer.
